{WEST knows there should be game, but doesn't know whether it will be 4\S, 
4\H or 3NT. To find out which she uses NMF and 
bids 2\C at her second turn.

EAST does not have a 4-card \H suit, nor does he have 
three \Ss, but he does have \Cs stopped so he bids 2NT, which West raises to 3NT.}

